t><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24237714/apple-intelligence-generative-ai-features-update-schedule" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24237714/apple-intelligence-generative-ai-features-update-schedule</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T15:59:21-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T15:59:21-04:00</updated><title>如何选择购买哪款 Apple Watch</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在彩色插图背景上渲染各种 Apple Watch 型号。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2khdyHiysXFCvt1JfQN-z5B3IfA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70781237/acastro_220321_5154_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;在 Apple Watch Series 10、Ultra 2 和第二代 SE 之间，有比以往更多的选择。我们将帮助您对它们进行分类。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se -best-smartwatch-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how-to</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T15:44:37-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T15:44:37-04:00</updated><title>美国终于瞄准了卡车膨胀问题</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;行人过马路&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IcRX_W-kzJrpLQjbL4Trzcc5-Ko=/0x1:4497x2999/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73577192/2169610326.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Bruce Bennett / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UrnuDv&quot;>;本周，美国国家公路交通安全国家公路交通安全管理局 (NHTSA) &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nhtsa.gov/press-releases/nhtsa-proposes-new-vehicle-safety-standard-protect-pedestrians&quot;>;提议新的车辆规则&lt;/ a>; 据称这将有助于减少美国的行人死亡。新规定似乎直接针对SUV和卡车日益大型化的趋势，事实证明，与中小型车辆相比，它们对行人的危害更大。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;G2j8Mo&quot;>;监管机构成立 50 多年以来，从未向汽车制造商发布过新规则，要求他们改变车辆设计，以更好地防止行人死亡。如果颁布，新规则可能会永久改变美国车辆的设计方式。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;zULZJF&quot;>;“很高兴看到 NHTSA 承认短视地关注行人检测（这是不完美的）……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241047/nhtsa-rule-pedestrian-safety-fmvss-suv-truck-design&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241047/nhtsa-rule-pedestrian-safety-fmvss-suv-truck-design" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24241047/nhtsa-rule-pedestrian-safety-fmvss-suv-truck-design</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry></feed>